{"service_name": "Value and Benefit Management", "service_id": "7727235402854979", "company_name": "Selex ES Ltd", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Selex ES Ltd\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Value and Benefit Management\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Selex ES offers Value based Programme and Project Management, a methodology to create Value for the Client based on BS EN 12973:2000 and gives an end to end framework for business improvement and consultancy problem solving which allows better business decisions with a clear auditable rationale.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Creation of Value for the Client\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     A framework for business improvement and consultancy problem solving\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Creative teamwork involving key employees and stakeholders\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Planning via a Work Plan\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Functional Analysis Systems Technique (FAST)\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     How is it being delivered, how can it be improved\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Can improve services, projects, processes and products\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Integrates a wide range of tools and techniques\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Programme management via a VBM steering group\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     British Standard BS EN 12973:2000 Value Management\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Clearer objectives, more closely aligned with business needs\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Better business decisions, with a clear rationale\n 